Note over datagrid: User clicks "Zoom To" 
 on unselected row datagrid->datagridClickHandler:onZoomTo(map.extent.clone(), 
 zoomToGraphic) Note over datagridClickHandler: Based on graphic type 
 centers the map datagridClickHandler->map: map.center_and_zoom 
 map.set_extent
datagridClickHandler->datagrid:datagrid.zoomlightrow_show Note over datagrid: Remebers row to highlight later 
 does not scroll
Note over map: Map finishes 
 zooming/panning map->datagridClickHandler:executes callback Note over datagridClickHandler: Callback datagridClickHandler->featureHighlighter:featureHighlighter.zoomlight_show Note over featureHighlighter: Highlights a zoom to feature featureHighlighter->maptips:maptips.show Note over maptips:Shows a zoomto maptip
map->bootstrapper:map.update_end
bootstrapper->datagrid:datagrid.apply_extent_filter Note over datagrid:Scrolls to and 
 highlights selected row
Note over datagrid: ---------- //// ----------
Note over datagrid: User clicks "Zoom To" 
 on a selected row datagrid-->>datagridClickHandler:onZoomBack() datagridClickHandler-->>map: map.set_extent Note over map: Zooms to previous extent datagridClickHandler-->>featureHighlighter: featureHighlighter.zoomlight_hide Note over featureHighlighter: Hides the highlighted 
 zoom feature datagridClickHandler-->>datagrid: datagrid.zoomlightrow_hide Note over datagrid: Removes selected row 
 from memory
map-->>bootstrapper:map.update_end bootstrapper-->>datagrid:datagrid.apply_extent_filter Note over datagrid:Updates grid content
